name: Leila in Trip
description: actually this photo is taken in lei's dream. the buildings and neighborhood are like just as she wanted. she walk around the neighborhood so happy and taking some pictures. and getting ready to go to beach for chillin. but she's so high af -as always- and dont remember the way of the beach haha. she also don't like crowded times that's because she decided to walk around at 06.30 a.m. she is so happy when she is alone. because she doesn't keep up with anybody and her only close friend is way too long. but the dream also become a nightmare because she doesn't like zeplins and baloons because of her fear of heights and anxiety. as u see in this picture she just try not to look at the things in the air. anyway.. just hope the dream is not become a nightmare. happy trips in a trippy day u all!
